title_bed_bats_review: Bed and breakfast in Rudijala · 10 bedrooms · 10 beds · 10 baths
listing_description: Lake Side Resort Neermahal, located on the banks of Rudrasagar Lake, is the perfect leisure destination near Agartala. Flanked by lush flora, and offering views of the magnificent Neermahal, this scenic water palace built by the erstwhile Maharaja of Tripura Kingdom, is the only resort in Melaghar to provide high-end facilities and services to its guests. Polo Lake Resort, Neermahal, is located 53 kilometres away from Agartala.
